Available Tools: send_sms | send_bulk_sms | get_sms_status | get_sms_history
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": "string", "message": "string", "from": "string" }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "to": "string", "status": "string", "cost": number, "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Send a verification code to a new user in London.
Call: { "func_call": "send_sms", "to": "+442079460123", "message": "Your VerifyNow code is 849201. Valid for 10 mins.", "from": "VerifyNow" }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_uk_9928374", "to": "+442079460123", "status": "sent", "cost": 0.045, "timestamp": "2023-10-27T14:02:11Z" }

